### Which @angular/* package(s) are relevant/related to the feature request?

forms

### Description

I see we have implemented for formBuilder but I don't like the syntax, We should pass nonNullable as param instead of extending the nonNullable.

```
const fb = new FormBuilder()
const login = fb.group({
    email: '',
    password: '',
}, {nonNullable: true});
```

Also do support on FormGroup
 ```
 myForm = new FormGroup({
    name: new FormControl('indra',),
    work: new FormControl(true),
  }, {nonNullable: true});
```




### Proposed solution

Change the syntax 
```
const fb = new FormBuilder();
const login = fb.nonNullable.group({
    email: '',
    password: '',
});
```

To
 
```
const fb = new FormBuilder();
const login = fb.group({
    email: '',
    password: '',
}, {nonNullable: true});
```
Also do support on FormGroup

 ```
 myForm = new FormGroup({
    name: new FormControl('indra',),
    work: new FormControl(true),
  }, {nonNullable: true});
```

